{"tid":2510938,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[燒腦慎入]Portal Reloaded真係神作","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T13:44:05.000Z","uid":257658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9de5457ce0edb60c3fd69dcd0ea468f86a33b286","tid":2510938,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"可能各位巴打都有玩過Portal 1,2.<br />\n部分人覺得好容易.<br />\n轉眼間Portal 2出左十年. 有community group出左隻Portal Reloaded.<br />\n加多一個新Portal Time portal.<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets2.rockpapershotgun.com/portal-reloaded.jpg/BROK/resize/1920%3E/format/jpg/quality/80/portal-reloaded.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets2.rockpapershotgun.com%2Fportal-reloaded.jpg%2FBROK%2Fresize%2F1920%253E%2Fformat%2Fjpg%2Fquality%2F80%2Fportal-reloaded.jpg&h=50b5b32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你可以Time Travel去同一個場境20年之後.<br />\n例如:<br />\n呢度通關既門set左Timer 20年之後先會開.<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRdeGZBzuNV6LKLSHR8sJ1csGVECYdXcMMWRAR8Nq1ubp?filename=ojevDQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojevDQX.png&h=141ba255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n所有你有2個選擇:<br />\n1. 係到等20年 (唔知有無成就<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢)<br />\n2. 用Time Portal back to future. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n使用time portal 回到20年後.<br />\n原來度門已經爛左. 過關. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdKaACXFmXu3rHBoD8GKeatkLHKGgqHwc9AqPFq2QeFi3?filename=MDxQDRs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDxQDRs.png&h=d1086de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且現在可以改變未來. E果舊方塊 現在既位置 會改變方塊未來既位置.<br />\n但現在既方塊 唔可以E過去未來. 因為唔符合laws of causality<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPEgnC44AmXPyqzV5NchmagU6pV1AnvANQJBDtCQ2h4My?filename=CNhQERp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCNhQERp.gif&h=59d65637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔劇透太多. 有興趣可以Google下."},{"pid":"aa8347b1f94581d86782a2f4f339785015b10412","tid":2510938,"uid":168384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9dce3405fbd0d9a983b766ef024c3172f9a11487","tid":2510938,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 令我唸起 一世都玩唔到既slient hill pt <br />\n<img src=\"https://cdna.artstation.com/p/assets/images/images/010/345/626/large/szymon-niewolski-highresscreenshot00016.jpg?1523939620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdna.artstation.com%2Fp%2Fassets%2Fimages%2Fimages%2F010%2F345%2F626%2Flarge%2Fszymon-niewolski-highresscreenshot00016.jpg%3F1523939620&h=5ee06467&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"123fe66aff7e5135845f35b7929b5302f83ac7cb","tid":2510938,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:44:05.000Z","msg":"cannot count to 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}